OL,3,CSmall firms urge Ofgem to act over
OL,4,Cspiralling energy standing charges on
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FA growing number of small businesses
OL,8,Fare complaining of vastly inflated
OL,9,Fstanding charges on top of their
OL,10,Fstandard energy bills, some as much as
OL,11,F13 times the level of three years ago.
OL,13,FThe Federation of Small Businesses
OL,14,F(FSB) has written to Ofgem, urging it
OL,15,Fto act over fast-growing standing
OL,16,Fcharges paid by small companies,
OL,17,Fparticularly those in rural areas.
