OL,3,CSmall firms urge Ofgem to act over
OL,4,Cspiralling energy standing charges on
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FOne business owner got in touch with
OL,8,Fthe group to report an increased
OL,9,Fstanding charge, from 70.94p per day
OL,10,Fin July 2021 to 969.64p per day in
OL,11,FSeptember 2023, more than 13 times
OL,12,Fhigher.
OL,14,FStanding charges are applied daily,
OL,15,Fregardless of how much energy the
OL,16,Fcustomer uses, and are used to cover
OL,17,Fthe cost of supplying energy to homes
OL,18,Fand businesses.
