OL,7,FThey also cover the costs of building
OL,8,Fnew network infrastructure and keeping
OL,9,Fthe power on when energy suppliers go
OL,10,Fbust.
OL,12,FWhile consumers' bills are limited by
OL,13,Fthe energy price cap, small
OL,14,Fbusinesses' are not.
