OL,3,CSmall firms urge Ofgem to act over
OL,4,Cspiralling energy standing charges on
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FTina McKenzie, FSB policy chairwoman,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We want Ofgem to do a thorough
OL,9,Freview of standing charges for
OL,10,Fbusinesses as well as consumers, for
OL,11,Fbetter transparency and to discern
OL,12,Fwhether energy companies are behaving
OL,13,Ffairly towards their small firm
OL,14,Fclients.
