OL,3,CSmall firms urge Ofgem to act over
OL,4,Cspiralling energy standing charges on
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,F"Small business energy customers
OL,8,Fbehave in a way more akin to consumers
OL,9,Fthan big businesses, lacking the
OL,10,Fresources, the expertise and the
OL,11,Fbuying power necessary to get the best
OL,12,Fpossible deal out of their energy
OL,13,Fsuppliers.
OL,15,F"However, they do not benefit from
OL,16,Fanything like the same level of
OL,17,Fprotection as that rightly available
OL,18,Fto households, leaving them caught
OL,19,Fbetween two stools.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
