OL,3,CSmall firms urge Ofgem to act over
OL,4,Cspiralling energy standing charges on
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,F"Many small businesses could be
OL,8,Fforgiven for suspecting that they have
OL,9,Fbeen seen as something of a soft
OL,10,Ftarget for price hikes in their
OL,11,Fstanding charges, and they do not have
OL,12,Fa full picture of where the money they
OL,13,Fpay on a daily basis is going `
OL,14,Fsomething that needs to change."
OL,16,FLate last year, Ofgem called for views
OL,17,Fon standing charges, which prompted
OL,18,Fmore than 20,000 people to respond.
