OL,3,CSmall firms urge Ofgem to act over
OL,4,Cspiralling energy standing charges on
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe regulator has said it wanted to
OL,8,Fopen a debate about how the charges
OL,9,Fwork, and welcomed opinions on how to
OL,10,Fchange the system.
OL,12,FStanding charges are often higher in
OL,13,Frural areas, where the cost per home
OL,14,Fto the energy supplier is higher.
OL,16,FThe FSB said this meant the charges
OL,17,Fwere disproportionately affecting
OL,18,Fbusinesses in rural areas.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/8
