OL,7,FThis is exacerbating the divide
OL,8,Fbetween rural and urban areas, the
OL,9,Fgroup said, and "(undermines) efforts
OL,10,Fto level up more remote parts of the
OL,11,FUK".
OL,13,FThe PA news agency has contacted Ofgem
OL,14,Ffor comment.
